# Copy to `.env.local` and fill in secrets:
#
#   cp .env.example .env.local   # macOS / Linux / Git Bash
#   copy .env.example .env.local # Windows CMD
#
# Then edit `.env.local` with your Supabase, Resend, Airtable, Zapier, and Stripe values.
# Membership checkout also needs:
#   STRIPE_TREETOTS_MEMBERSHIP_MONTHLY_PRICE_ID=
#   STRIPE_TREETOTS_MEMBERSHIP_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID=
# Run `npm run env:check` and open `/admin/settings/launch-readiness` after staff login.
